      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg type="letterhead" rend="left"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00007"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date>12. X. 1905</date></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb133">Wien,
                        XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></seg></opener><p><salute>lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute> beifolgd 2 Sitze zur <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35077" subtype="implied"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29843">Kakadupremière</rs></rs>. – Ob ich morgen den Sitz
               zum <rs type="event" ref="#pmb305697"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29903">Zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>piel</rs></rs> an Ihren <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04020-1"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb24648" subtype="implied">Bruder</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>enden ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04020-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L04017" subtype="See"/>.</note>, wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich in
               diesem Moment noch nicht ganz<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>icher; we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> nicht diesmal,
               näch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Woche be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ti<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t.</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
